Package com.cafean.JobStatus

Class StreamContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cafean.JobStatus.StreamContext
  • public class StreamContext
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the context information related to a job stream environment. StreamContext contains platform information and a tracker module reference so that a streams unique platform can be identified, and additional information can be queried.
